  How to explain the "Formula" to Judges:
  If a judge asks: "Is the AI just giving a random score?"
  Your Answer:
  > "No. We use a Recursive Validation Logic.
  > 1. The AI provides a Semantic Score based on the answer content.
  > 2. Our Scoring Engine (scoring.js) then weights that score against the Interview Velocity.
  > 3. If a candidate is fast-tracked (1 question), they get a 'Confidence Bonus.'
  > 4. If they require a 'Probe' (follow-up), the engine applies a Strictness Filter to ensure they actually proved their depth before awarding a 'Strong'
  verdict."

