   1. app.js (User clicks button) $\rightarrow$
   2. agent.js (Brain decides which skill to test) $\rightarrow$
   3. aiProvider.js (AI generates the specific question) $\rightarrow$
   4. scoring.js (Judge calculates the final gap analysis).

